    Command for writing the results of query to file system.

    The syntax of using this command in SQL is: 

    
   INSERT OVERWRITE [LOCAL] DIRECTORY
   path
   [ROW FORMAT row_format]
   [STORED AS file_format]
   SELECT ...

    param: isLocal whether the path specified in storage is a local directory param: storage storage format used to describe how the query result is stored. param: query the logical plan representing data to write to param: overwrite whether overwrites existing directory
